T02TD1566E:237a-0: @237a // de nas bya rog la sogs pa'i gtor ma'i sngags bri pa ni /
T02TD1566E:237a-1: aom klam klam klam / dharmma t'a /
T02TD1566E:237a-4: b'a ya sa na: kam b'a ya /
T02TD1566E:237a-10: k'a ka / ba lim grihna ta /
T02TD1566E:237a-13: // / aom shlam shlam shlam / aa pra tishtha /
T02TD1566E:237a-17: siddhi shu na k'a / sam t'a /
T02TD1566E:237a-27: da sh'a sh'a sh'a ts'a ri na /
T02TD1566E:237a-37: bhrim bhrim bhrim bh'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD1566E:237a-39: // / aom aom aom hrom hrom hrom phegs k'a ra /
T02TD1566E:237a-40: phegs ka ri na: ku la phra /
T02TD1566E:237a-50: // / tshes bcur me tog rnams kyis ni //
T02TD1566E:237a-51: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma la mchod //
T02TD1566E:237a-52: dar gyi lag gdub sbyin par bya //
T02TD1566E:237a-53: grub pa'i rdzas chen mar dang bcas //
T02TD1566E:237a-54: til nas kyis ni gsang sa ru //
T02TD1566E:237a-55: sbyin sreg bzlas pa do shal sbyin //
T02TD1566E:237a-56: mkha' sdigs byed pa'i phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1566E:237a-57: phyag rgya chen po dang bcas pa'i //
T02TD1566E:237a-58: ri khrod dbang phyug snying pos bsdus //
T02TD1566E:237b-0: @237b pandi ta klu'i sbyin pa'i rnal 'byor gyis snying po'i don bsdus pa bstan pa'o //
T02TD1566E:237b-1: grub pa thob pa'i gnas drang srong srin po rir rgya gar shar phyogs kyi pandi ta chen po d'a na sh'i las lha'i skad las bod kyi skad du rang 'gyur du mdzad pa'o//
